narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 111 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 111 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: If you think you're reading for French 130, you should probably take French 120.

an intensive language course that exposes you to a lot of cool books/films. You become very close to your classmates and it is a fun community. You should take it if you are interested in french and french culture.
